# Ratchet-down: each retirement MR (problem record
# 2026-05-02-ios-humble-ui-deep-retirement, G1) deletes both the view
# file and its entry below. The destination is the platform-required
# subset only.
#
# One filename per line. Lines starting with `#` and blank lines
# ignored.
